Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.69,0:09:08.75,1080P-sgsm-50,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur4\move(-20,10,10,10,0,500)}指命名应该是根据火星的卫星，也就是希腊神话，而不是这俩词的本意来命名的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.33,0:00:05.88,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Hello it's Scott Manley here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.33,0:00:05.88,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你好 我是Scott Manley
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.18,0:00:09.37,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Last week Blue Origin completed the 14th test flight
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.18,0:00:09.37,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}上周蓝色起源完成了第14次
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.39,0:00:14.25,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}of their reusable sub-orbital launch vehicle and capsule New Shepard.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.39,0:00:14.25,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}他们的可重复使用的亚轨道运载火箭和载人舱新谢泼德的试飞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.32,0:00:18.49,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}And this was actually a new vehicle for both the capsule and the booster.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.32,0:00:18.49,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这次试飞实际上使用了全新的载人舱和助推器
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.52,0:00:21.31,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}It's only the fourth booster they've built in this program.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.52,0:00:21.31,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这只是他们在这个项目中建造的第四个助推器
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.73,0:00:27.19,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}And as I understand it there's a pretty good chance they will be carrying passengers later this year
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.73,0:00:27.19,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}据我所知 他们很有可能在今年晚些时候搭载乘客
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.36,0:00:31.67,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}while of course in parallel they're still working on their New Glenn launch vehicle
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.36,0:00:31.67,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}同时 他们还在研制新格伦运载火箭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.67,0:00:35.04,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}which is going to be absolutely massive.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.67,0:00:35.04,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而这将绝对是庞大的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.26,0:00:38.71,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Blue Origin is of course Jeff Bezos rocket company
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.26,0:00:38.71,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}蓝色起源当然是那个Jeff Bezos的火箭公司
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.71,0:00:42.03,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}and that of course brings parallels to SpaceX.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.71,0:00:42.03,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这当然会给SpaceX带来相似之处
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.06,0:00:46.42,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}You've got your pair of tech billionaires spending money building rocket ships
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.06,0:00:46.42,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}有这么一对科技领域的亿万富翁在花钱造火箭和飞船
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.47,0:00:48.78,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}because that's what was cool when they were growing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.47,0:00:48.78,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}因为在他们成长的过程中 这才是最酷的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.98,0:00:51.94,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}But Blue Origin was actually founded before SpaceX.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.98,0:00:51.94,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但其实蓝色起源成立的时间比SpaceX还要早
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.98,0:00:53.28,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}It's been around a lot longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.98,0:00:53.28,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}它已经存在很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.46,0:00:56.26,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}And yet it's still only doing this suborbital thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.46,0:00:56.26,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但它目前还只是在做亚轨道的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.67,0:01:00.00,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}The company's motto is {\i1}gratitum ferociter{\i0} right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.67,0:01:00.00,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}公司的座右铭是{\i1}gratitum ferociter{\i0} (拉丁语) 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.00,0:01:02.38,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Step by step ferociously.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.00,0:01:02.38,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}意思是一步步凶猛地发展
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.71,0:01:05.66,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}But their development has sort of taken a different tack.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.71,0:01:05.66,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但他们的发展却采取了不同的策略
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.69,0:01:09.18,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}They've started by building very small rocket engines
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.69,0:01:09.18,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}他们从制造非常小的火箭发动机开始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.21,0:01:13.11,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}and building up and developing technological experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.21,0:01:13.11,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}并积累和发展技术经验
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.27,0:01:16.00,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}The first engines they built were the BE-1.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.27,0:01:16.00,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}他们制造的第一台发动机是BE-1
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.00,0:01:18.15,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}And these are hydrogen peroxide engines.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.00,0:01:18.15,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而这些都是过氧化氢发动机
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.15,0:01:22.23,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}The hydrogen peroxide decomposes to oxygen and steam
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.15,0:01:22.23,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}双氧水分解成氧气和蒸汽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.47,0:01:27.52,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}and it's sort of the first project that a lot of people do when they're learning to build rockets.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.47,0:01:27.52,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这也是很多人在学习建造火箭时的第一个项目
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.66,0:01:32.21,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Peter Beck of Rocket Lab if you remember built a rocket bike powered by these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.66,0:01:32.21,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fs60}火箭实验室的Peter Beck 如果你还记得的话 他造了一辆由这些东西驱动的火箭自行车
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.55,0:01:35.92,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}The BE-1 had a thrust of about one tonne
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.55,0:01:35.92,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}BE-1的推力约为1吨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.92,0:01:39.60,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}and they used nine of them to fly their first test vehicle
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.92,0:01:39.60,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}他们用其中的九台发动机驱动第一枚测试火箭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.75,0:01:44.15,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}and demonstrating not only ascent but descent and soft landing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.75,0:01:44.15,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}并验证了上升 下降 还有软着陆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.19,0:01:48.02,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}and this is a sort of theme that we've seen with all of Blue Origins vehicles.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.19,0:01:48.02,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这也是我们在所有蓝色起源运载火箭上看到的一种主题
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.64,0:01:54.09,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Blue Origin have never built a launch vehicle without recovery and reuse capability.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.64,0:01:54.09,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}蓝色起源从未制造过没有回收和重复使用能力的运载火箭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.63,0:01:56.66,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}The BE-2 was their next step up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.63,0:01:56.66,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}BE-2是他们的下一步发展
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.69,0:01:58.15,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}this was a pump fed engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.69,0:01:58.15,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这是一个泵循环发动机
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.15,0:02:01.60,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}It used peroxide and RP-1 liquid propellants.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.15,0:02:01.60,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}它使用过氧化物和RP-1液体推进剂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.81,0:02:03.86,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}It generated about 14 tons of thrust
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.81,0:02:03.86,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}产生了大约14吨的推力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.87,0:02:08.31,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}and they fit five of them onto a test vehicle called the PM2.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.87,0:02:08.31,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}他们把其中的5台装进了一枚叫PM2的测试火箭中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.19,0:02:12.23,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}So yeah this is some footage from their very first test flight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.19,0:02:12.23,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以这是他们第一次试飞的一些视频
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.23,0:02:13.68,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}It was a short hop.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.23,0:02:13.68,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这是一个短暂的跳跃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.81,0:02:16.48,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}They only lit three of the engines on ascent
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.81,0:02:16.48,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}他们在上升时只点燃了三台发动机
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.48,0:02:19.52,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}and then shut down to two of the engines for descent
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.48,0:02:19.52,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}然后下降时只点燃两台发动机
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.75,0:02:23.30,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}but even then they still have to have throttle capabilities to be able to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.75,0:02:23.30,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但即使如此 他们仍然必须有节流能力才能做到这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.76,0:02:29.26,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Now on the second flight they lit all five engines and they wanted to start picking up speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.76,0:02:29.26,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那么在第二次飞行时 他们点燃了所有五台发动机 他们想开始加速
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.66,0:02:35.59,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}As the vehicle went supersonic at about mach 1.2, it developed aerodynamic instability.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.66,0:02:35.59,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}当飞行器以1.2马赫的速度进入超音速状态时 出现了气动力不稳的现象
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.79,0:02:38.31,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}They lost control of the vehicle, shut down the engines.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.79,0:02:38.31,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}他们失去了对飞行器的控制 关闭了发动机
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.46,0:02:39.42,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}And that was the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.46,0:02:39.42,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就这样结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.50,0:02:44.02,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}It was only two flights for this vehicle even although it was designed to be reusable.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.50,0:02:44.02,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这架飞行器只进行了两次飞行 尽管它的设计是可以重复使用的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.55,0:02:50.06,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}So their third engine was the BE-3 and they switched over to hydrogen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.55,0:02:50.06,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以他们的第三台发动机是BE-3 改用了液氢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.30,0:02:54.62,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}So hydrogen's a cryogenic propellant and it's very difficult to work with.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.30,0:02:54.62,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那么液氢是一种非常难用的低温推进剂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.88,0:02:58.85,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}SpaceX has not developed a hydrogen engine internally.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.88,0:02:58.85,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}SpaceX内部并没有开发出液氢发动机
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.30,0:03:02.56,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}They also chose an engine design that nobody else had managed to fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.30,0:03:02.56,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}蓝色起源还选择了一种别人没试飞过的发动机设计
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.56,0:03:05.16,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}It's called the combustion tap off cycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.56,0:03:05.16,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这叫做抽气循环
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.36,0:03:10.15,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}So in a regular rocket engine you need to power those turbo pumps with hot gas
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.36,0:03:10.15,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那么在普通的火箭发动机中 你需要用热气为那些涡轮泵提供动力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.15,0:03:15.66,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}and you'll typically have a pre-burner or a gas generator that generates this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.15,0:03:15.66,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你通常会有一个预燃烧器 或者气体发生器 来产生这些热气
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.70,0:03:17.63,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}So you've got a second combustion chamber.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.70,0:03:17.63,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那么这样就需要第二个燃烧室
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.92,0:03:19.52,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}But in the tap off cycle,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.92,0:03:19.52,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但在抽气循环中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.54,0:03:26.31,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}they just say well why not just have a pipe that drains high pressure gas from the combustion chamber
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.54,0:03:26.31,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}他们只是说 为什么不干脆有一个管道 从燃烧室排出高压气体
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.56,0:03:27.84,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}and uses that to run the turbine
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.56,0:03:27.84,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}并利用它来运行涡轮机
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.84,0:03:29.68,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}so you get rid of some stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.84,0:03:29.68,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那么这样可以去除一些部件
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.05,0:03:32.48,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}So in theory the engine is simpler and lighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.05,0:03:32.48,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以理论上来说 发动机会更简单 更轻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.48,0:03:33.76,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Of course it's harder to build
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.48,0:03:33.76,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}当然 这种发动机其实更难制造
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.76,0:03:38.34,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}because you can't independently control the temperature for your turbines.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.76,0:03:38.34,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}因为你无法独立控制涡轮的温度
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.82,0:03:41.51,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}It means it's much harder to get deep throttling.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.82,0:03:41.51,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这就意味着要想深度节流的话就难得多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.66,0:03:47.27,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}And the BE-3 actually does have very good deep throttling capability.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.66,0:03:47.27,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而BE-3实际上有着非常好的深度节流能力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.58,0:03:51.28,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}It's able to go from 100 percent down to below 20 percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.58,0:03:51.28,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}它能够从100%节流到20%以下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.50,0:03:54.23,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}And this means that unlike the Falcon 9
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.50,0:03:54.23,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这意味着与猎鹰9号是不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.62,0:04:00.93,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}which has to perform this hoverslam suicide burn by shutting down all but one of its nine engines
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.62,0:04:00.93,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}猎鹰9号是只启动一台发动机 来进行这种悬停猛击式的自杀式点火
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.20,0:04:04.76,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}this uses the same single engine on the way up and way down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.20,0:04:04.76,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而新谢泼德上升和下降的过程中使用相同的单台发动机
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.09,0:04:07.90,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}It can throttle deeply enough that it can hover
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.09,0:04:07.90,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}它可以深度节流 推力小到足以在空中悬停
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.29,0:04:12.67,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}and slew across and land all back on the landing site.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.29,0:04:12.67,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}并且水平飞行一段距离 然后着陆到着陆场
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.30,0:04:19.69,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fs37}And it's not the only thing about New Shepard that makes it look like something you would build to get engineering experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.30,0:04:19.69,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}除此之外 新谢泼德上还有一些特征是为了得到工程经验
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.06,0:04:24.08,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}The aerodynamics are very much different from any other vehicle I've seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.06,0:04:24.08,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}它的气动力学外形与我见过的任何其他飞行器都有很大的不同
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.75,0:04:27.03,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Obviously the booster has the capsule sitting on top.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.75,0:04:27.03,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}很明显 助推器的顶部有一个载人舱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.06,0:04:31.60,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}But once the capsule's gone it has this big annular ring-shaped fin
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.06,0:04:31.60,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但一旦载人舱消失 就会变成一个大的环形翼面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.60,0:04:38.66,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}and attached to that you see these air brakes that pop out during descent to control and slow things down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.60,0:04:38.66,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}附在上面的减速板在下降过程中会弹出 以控制并减慢速度
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.69,0:04:43.04,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}So that it has more controllable deceleration during return from space
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.69,0:04:43.04,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这样它在从太空返回时的减速就更可控了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.04,0:04:45.97,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}and a little extra braking during the landing procedure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.04,0:04:45.97,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}并在着陆过程中进行额外的制动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.44,0:04:49.12,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}The capsule on top of course it detaches
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.44,0:04:49.12,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在顶部的载人舱 当然就会分离出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.12,0:04:53.19,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}and it uses parachutes for its descent and ultimate landing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.12,0:04:53.19,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}并使用降落伞进行下降和最终的着陆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.42,0:05:00.15,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}It has a small rocket engine that slows it down from like 15 miles an hour to five miles an hour
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.42,0:05:00.15,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}它有一个小型的火箭发动机 可以使速度从每小时24公里下降到每小时8公里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.38,0:05:03.91,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}and there's also a ring of aluminium honeycomb crush core
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.38,0:05:03.91,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而且还有一圈铝制蜂窝粉碎芯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.04,0:05:07.68,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}so that if they hit too hard it will absorb a lot of the kinetic energy
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.04,0:05:07.68,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这样如果他们撞得太狠 就会吸收很多动能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.89,0:05:10.98,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}and avoid real damage to the capsule structure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.89,0:05:10.98,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}并避免对载人舱结构造成实际损害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.33,0:05:14.59,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Since the capsule is supposed to be a crew vehicle
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.33,0:05:14.59,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}由于载人舱应该是一个载人飞行器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.88,0:05:17.08,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}it comes with a launch escape system
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.88,0:05:17.08,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以它带有发射逃逸系统
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.10,0:05:20.95,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}which will push the capsule away from the booster if anything goes wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.10,0:05:20.95,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}如果出了问题 它将把载人舱推离助推器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.42,0:05:24.96,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}This escape motor is not built by Blue Origin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.42,0:05:24.96,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这个逃逸发动机不是蓝色起源制造的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.19,0:05:28.50,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}The escape motor as I understand it comes from Aerojet Rocketdyne.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.19,0:05:28.50,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}据我所知 逃逸发动机来自阿罗杰特洛克达因公司
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.59,0:05:33.03,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}It's a high thrust solid rocket motor that can be replaced.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.59,0:05:33.03,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这是一个可以更换的推力大的固体火箭发动机 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.12,0:05:38.96,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}If you look inside the capsule, there's a sort of a plinth that comes up in the middle of the vehicle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.12,0:05:38.96,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}如果你看载人舱内部 有一个像是基座的东西 在航天器的中间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.96,0:05:41.39,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}That's where the rocket motor is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.96,0:05:41.39,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那就是火箭发动机的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.77,0:05:44.33,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}So the capsule can escape at max q
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.77,0:05:44.33,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那么载人舱可以在最大气动压力的状态下逃逸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.34,0:05:49.62,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}that was the demonstration here and perform a safe return to the the earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.34,0:05:49.62,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}正如这里的验证发射的画面一样 并安全返回地球
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.24,0:05:55.68,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Now the booster in that case they were not sure whether the booster would survive
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.24,0:05:55.68,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那么在这种情况下 他们不确定助推器是否能扛下来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.68,0:06:00.06,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}because the boosters going at transonic speeds under full power
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.68,0:06:00.06,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}因为助推器发动机正以全功率的状态运行在跨音速阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.57,0:06:04.06,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}and the aerodynamics are obviously changing at that moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.57,0:06:04.06,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而空气动力学显然在那一刻发生了变化
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.08,0:06:08.31,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}they fully expected that there was a pretty good chance the booster would be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.08,0:06:08.31,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}他们完全可以预料到 助推器有相当大的可能会被摧毁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.35,0:06:13.44,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}It would either flip out a control or perhaps the rocket motor might damage the front of the vehicle
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.35,0:06:13.44,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}火箭要么会失控 要么会被载人舱的固体火箭损坏前面的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.98,0:06:15.54,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}and that would develop into something worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.98,0:06:15.54,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那会变得更糟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.58,0:06:21.82,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}But no. The booster performed this wonderful deceleration, descent
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.58,0:06:21.82,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是没有 助推器很好地进行了减速和下降的过程
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.88,0:06:24.38,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}and landing back where it was supposed to
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.88,0:06:24.38,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}并落回了它应该着陆的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.42,0:06:26.63,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}which is good job team.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.42,0:06:26.63,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}他们团队做得不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.26,0:06:31.62,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Now there is a second version of the BE-3, the BE-3U
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.26,0:06:31.62,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那么BE-3有了第二个版本 BE-3U
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.62,0:06:35.86,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}which is going to be the second stage of the New Glenn rocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.62,0:06:35.86,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这将是新格伦火箭的二级
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.40,0:06:38.99,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}And the U means upper stage obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.40,0:06:38.99,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而U显然是指上面级
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.44,0:06:44.72,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}The engine design instead using the combustion tap off, it's an expander cycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.44,0:06:44.72,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}发动机的设计 不是抽气循环 而是膨胀循环
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.84,0:06:48.47,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}An expander cycles, you take the very cold liquid hydrogen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.84,0:06:48.47,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}膨胀循环是指 你把非常冷的液氢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.47,0:06:52.24,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}You run it over heat exchanger so it takes heat from the combustion
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.47,0:06:52.24,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}通过热交换器 这样就能从燃烧室获得热量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.38,0:06:53.89,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}and it wants to vaporize
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.38,0:06:53.89,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}使之蒸发
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.01,0:06:57.38,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}and that's allowed to expand through the turbine which drives the pumps
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.01,0:06:57.38,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}并通过驱动泵的涡轮机进行膨胀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.42,0:07:00.28,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}and you get a pretty high performance engine from this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.42,0:07:00.28,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}然后从中得到一个性能相当高的发动机
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.78,0:07:06.56,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}So this is similar to the RL-10 engine that's already used on the upper stage of Atlas and Delta IV.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.78,0:07:06.56,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那么 这与宇宙神和德尔塔四上面级已经使用的RL-10发动机类似
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.65,0:07:08.78,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}But it's an open cycle version
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.65,0:07:08.78,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但这是一个开式循环的版本
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.81,0:07:11.63,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}so it's not as efficient but it gets a lot more thrust.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.81,0:07:11.63,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以它的效率不高 但推力更大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.04,0:07:15.39,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}So while New Glenn is going to use these for its second stage
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.04,0:07:15.39,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以 当新格伦打算用这些东西来做第二级的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.52,0:07:19.07,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}the Vulcan built by ULA is going to stick to the RL-10
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.52,0:07:19.07,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}ULA制造的火神火箭将坚持使用RL-10
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.11,0:07:24.87,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}but both rockets are going to use the BE-4 engines which have been developed by Blue Origin
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.11,0:07:24.87,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但这两枚火箭都将使用蓝色起源研发的BE-4发动机(作为一级发动机)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.90,0:07:28.72,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}and this is a staged combustion cycle methane engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.90,0:07:28.72,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而这是一个分级燃烧循环的甲烷发动机
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.72,0:07:32.40,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}It gets more thrust than the Raptor but it's not a full flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.72,0:07:32.40,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}它的推力比猛禽大 但不是全流量分级燃烧循环
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.40,0:07:33.28,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Let's be clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.40,0:07:33.28,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}明确地说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.40,0:07:39.01,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}It's just a regular staged combustion cycle getting great thrust and great performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.40,0:07:39.01,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这只是一个普通的分级燃烧循环 有着巨大的推力和强大的性能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.38,0:07:40.96,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}So if all goes according to plan
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.38,0:07:40.96,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以如果一切按计划进行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.18,0:07:46.31,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}we should see two of these powering the first flight of Vulcan later this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.18,0:07:46.31,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}今年晚些时候 我们应该能看到其中的两台为火神火箭的首飞提供动力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.83,0:07:50.17,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}And we should see seven of these powering New Glenn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.83,0:07:50.17,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而我们应该看到7个这样的发动机为新格伦提供动力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.48,0:07:53.44,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Now officially New Glenn is supposed to fly 2021.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.48,0:07:53.44,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那么新格伦应该在2021年正式飞行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.44,0:07:54.87,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I'm skeptical of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.44,0:07:54.87,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我对此持怀疑态度
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.87,0:08:00.68,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Because they've had trouble with delivering the engines on time for ULA's Vulcan
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.87,0:08:00.68,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}因为他们在为ULA的火神火箭按时交付发动机方面遇到了麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.03,0:08:04.74,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}and that's been pushed out to the fourth quarter of 2021.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.03,0:08:04.74,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而这已经被推到了2021年第四季度
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.17,0:08:07.87,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}It's entirely possible this has shifted to next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.17,0:08:07.87,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这完全有可能已经推移到了明年
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.15,0:08:10.54,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}But it would certainly be an ambitious vehicle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.15,0:08:10.54,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但它肯定会是一个艰巨的火箭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.59,0:08:14.88,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}It would be able to put more mass into low earth orbit than Falcon 9.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.59,0:08:14.88,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}它的近地轨道运载质量比猎鹰9号更大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.36,0:08:18.36,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}On paper it wouldn't be as capable as Falcon Heavy
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.36,0:08:18.36,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在纸面上 它的运力不如重型猎鹰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.41,0:08:21.68,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}but then again this has a much larger fairing
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.41,0:08:21.68,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但同样地 它的整流罩更大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.68,0:08:25.30,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}and Falcon Heavy is definitely limited by its fairing size.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.68,0:08:25.30,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而重型猎鹰绝对会受限于整流罩尺寸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.53,0:08:28.47,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}The first stage is supposed to be completely reusable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.53,0:08:28.47,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}一级应该是可以完全重复使用的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.47,0:08:29.58,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Has seven engines
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.47,0:08:29.58,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}拥有七台发动机
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.62,0:08:35.32,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}but it should only need one of those engines to get the thrust to mass ratio required for a landing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.62,0:08:35.32,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但应该只需要一台发动机就能获得着陆所需的推重比
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.79,0:08:40.52,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}They've actually acquired ships which are old car ferries I think
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.79,0:08:40.52,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}他们其实已经收购了一些船 我觉得这些船是旧的汽车渡轮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.91,0:08:44.74,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}which they're in the process of adapting into floating landing pads.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.91,0:08:44.74,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}他们正准备将其改造成浮动的着陆场
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.42,0:08:47.38,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Of course I'm saying this in the week after
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.42,0:08:47.38,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}当然 我是在那件事发生一周后说的这句话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.39,0:08:51.79,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}it's been revealed that SpaceX has bought a pair of old oil drilling platforms
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.39,0:08:51.79,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那件事就是SpaceX已经买下了一对旧的石油钻井平台
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.82,0:08:53.42,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}and plan to use those with Starship.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.82,0:08:53.42,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}并计划将其用于Starship
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.82,0:08:56.18,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}They are going to be called Phobos and Deimos.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.82,0:08:56.18,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}它们将被称为福波斯和得摩斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.20,0:09:00.16,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}And you guys are getting way too excited about an eccentric billionaire
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.20,0:09:00.16,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你们对一个古怪的亿万富翁太兴奋了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.30,0:09:05.44,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}who now owns a pair of offshore bases named fear and dread.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.30,0:09:05.44,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}他现在拥有一对名为{\i1}害怕{\i0} 和{\i1}恐惧{\i0} 的离岸基地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.69,0:09:08.75,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Yeah you guys should really be keeping up with your classical mythology
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.69,0:09:08.75,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是啊 你们真的应该跟上你们的古典神话了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.04,0:09:12.94,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}But anyway there's one other rocket engine that Blue Origin has developed
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.04,0:09:12.94,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但不管怎么说 蓝色起源还研发了一款火箭发动机
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.95,0:09:17.36,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}And it's the BE-7 which is designed for landing stuff on the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.95,0:09:17.36,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那就是为登陆月球而设计的BE-7
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.36,0:09:19.20,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}It's another hydrogen engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.36,0:09:19.20,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这是另一种液氢发动机
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.20,0:09:22.24,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}It's got deep throttle control. Uses the expander cycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.20,0:09:22.24,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}它使用膨胀循环 可以深度节流
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.44,0:09:27.20,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I think it's like a smaller and more efficient version of the BE-3U.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.44,0:09:27.20,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我认为它就像BE-3U的一个更小更高效的版本
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.54,0:09:31.68,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}And it's one of Blue Origin's core contributions to the National Team
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.54,0:09:31.68,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这也是蓝色起源对{\i1}国家队{\i0} (月球着陆器)的核心贡献之一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.73,0:09:35.60,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}which has made a bid for the Human Landing System or the Artemis Program.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.73,0:09:35.60,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}也就是为阿尔忒弥斯计划中的载人登月系统(HLS)竞标的方案
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.86,0:09:37.33,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}They're one of three finalists
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.86,0:09:37.33,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}他们是三个入围者之一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.41,0:09:41.02,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}and there is supposed to be a downselect decision made early this year
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.41,0:09:41.02,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而今年年初应该会淘汰掉一个方案
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.03,0:09:43.20,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}but I won't be surprised if that gets pushed out
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.03,0:09:43.20,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但如果HLS被砍了 我也不会惊讶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.26,0:09:46.77,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}since Congress hasn't really delivered the amount of money needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.26,0:09:46.77,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}因为国会还没有真正划出其所需的资金量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.84,0:09:53.13,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}And the primary driver behind the accelerated timeline is well no longer in the white house.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.84,0:09:53.13,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而加速的时间表背后的主要推动者已经不在白宫了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.59,0:09:56.72,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}But long before humans return to the surface of the moon
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.59,0:09:56.72,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但早在人类重返月球表面之前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.72,0:10:02.51,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Blue Origin is probably going to put stuff stuff on the surface using Blue Moon which is their lander
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.72,0:10:02.51,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}蓝色起源可能会用蓝月亮 也就是他们的着陆器 把东西放在月表上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.54,0:10:07.20,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}And that's part of NASA's commercial lunar payload services program or CLPS.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.54,0:10:07.20,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那是NASA商业月球有效载荷服务项目的一部分 简称CLPS
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.61,0:10:10.80,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}So yeah they can put payloads on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.61,0:10:10.80,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以是的 他们可以把有效载荷放在这上面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.96,0:10:11.78,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Take them to the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.96,0:10:11.78,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}把它们带到月表
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.82,0:10:14.50,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}They could be rovers experiments other hardware.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.82,0:10:14.50,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}可以是漫游车 实验品 其他设备等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.82,0:10:17.82,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}And that is powered again by the BE-7 engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.82,0:10:17.82,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而这也是由BE-7发动机提供动力的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.85,0:10:25.60,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}In fact the National Team's lander. It's essentially an extension of the Blue Moon spacecraft.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.85,0:10:25.60,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}事实上 国家队的登陆器 它本质上是蓝月亮航天器的延伸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.70,0:10:28.81,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}So that is the state of Blue Origin right now
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.70,0:10:28.81,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那么这就是蓝色起源现在的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.85,0:10:33.66,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}and many people point out they haven't been quite as aggressive or as fast as SpaceX
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.85,0:10:33.66,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而许多人指出 他们还没有像SpaceX那样激进或快速
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.68,0:10:37.80,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}but then again they haven't exploded as many rockets as SpaceX.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.68,0:10:37.80,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但话又说回来了 他们没有像SpaceX那样炸过很多火箭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.21,0:10:40.58,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}As far as I'm concerned they can take as long as they like
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.21,0:10:40.58,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在我看来 他们想花多长时间就花多长时间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.60,0:10:42.39,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}as long as they don't go out of businesses
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.60,0:10:42.39,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}只要不倒闭就行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.54,0:10:45.79,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}as long as they keep building rockets, they'll be interesting to look at.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.54,0:10:45.79,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}只要他们继续制造火箭 关注他们就很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.66,0:10:48.24,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}And it will be a fantastic moment
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.66,0:10:48.24,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而这将是一个美妙的时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.35,0:10:53.60,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}when paying members of the public can look at some of this hardware from the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.35,0:10:53.60,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}当为此花费的公众可以从内部看到这些设备的一些情况
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.67,0:10:55.83,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}And look down on the earth below them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.67,0:10:55.83,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}并看向着陆器下方的地面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.98,0:10:58.54,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I'm Scott Manley. Fly safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.98,0:10:58.54,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我是Scott Manley 切记 注意飞行安全
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.02,0:11:17.25,1080P-sgbd-4s,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}[Music]
